935
00:50:06,603 --> 00:50:07,916
On the phonograph.

936
00:50:07,916 --> 00:50:10,092
Oh. Well.

937
00:50:25,157 --> 00:50:25,939
What's that one?

938
00:50:28,095 --> 00:50:29,495
Never heard of it.

939
00:50:29,999 --> 00:50:31,350
