951
00:51:00,987 --> 00:51:02,711
Do I know Paris?

952
00:51:05,601 --> 00:51:07,350
Now is summertime.

953
00:51:07,402 --> 00:51:08,654
Champs-lyses.

954
00:51:08,695 --> 00:51:09,919
La Gare du Nord.

955
00:51:09,973 --> 00:51:11,995
The Opra, Boulevard des Capucines

956
00:51:13,220 --> 00:51:14,411
La Chapelle

957
00:51:14,453 --> 00:51:15,500
Rue Montmartre

958
00:51:15,531 --> 00:51:17,173
Boulevard de Rochechouart

959
00:51:17,230 --> 00:51:18,395
Rue Fontaine

960
00:51:18,451 --> 00:51:20,258
La Place Blanche.

961
00:51:23,370 --> 00:51:24,968
What a small world.

962
00:51:34,051 --> 00:51:34,894
Cigarette?

963
00:51:34,989 --> 00:51:35,563
Thanks.

964
00:51:38,727 --> 00:51:39,636
Got a light?

965
00:51:43,057 --> 00:51:45,824
We are a long way from home.

966
00:51:48,781 --> 00:51:49,664
Excuse me.

967
00:51:54,967 --> 00:51:55,689
Well?

968
00:51:56,556 --> 00:51:59,197
He still thinks he's playing his last card.

969
00:52:00,284 --> 00:52:01,110
Not bad.

970
00:52:01,186 --> 00:52:02,240
I'll tell her you said so.

971
00:52:02,289 --> 00:52:04,724
No no no. I mean the rock she's wearing.

972
00:52:04,763 --> 00:52:08,619
Now if it was me, I'd get them first and then do the fancy stuff afterward.

973
00:52:08,619 --> 00:52:09,435
Shut up

974
00:52:09,435 --> 00:52:11,283
You can't talk to me like that.

975
00:52:11,283 --> 00:52:12,558
You heard me. Shut up.

976
00:52:15,853 --> 00:52:17,246
Okay.

977
00:52:20,496 --> 00:52:22,027
He was talking about me.

978
00:52:22,071 --> 00:52:23,317
He was worried about you.

979
00:52:23,362 --> 00:52:24,359
About me?

980
00:52:24,399 --> 00:52:25,943
All that stuff you're holding.

981
00:52:27,289 --> 00:52:28,426
That's nice of him.

982
00:52:28,464 --> 00:52:29,748
You're not worried yourself?

983
00:52:29,825 --> 00:52:31,117
No.

984
00:52:31,675 --> 00:52:33,111
Not while I'm with you.

985
00:52:35,448 --> 00:52:36,101
Right.

986
00:52:38,578 --> 00:52:39,714
This is something.

987
00:52:39,714 --> 00:52:42,688
Isn't it? And it hardly weighs anything.

988
00:52:45,228 --> 00:52:46,074
At least

989
00:52:46,074 --> 00:52:47,911
20,000 francs.

990
00:52:47,911 --> 00:52:49,231
Add a zero.

991
00:52:49,231 --> 00:52:52,248
I mean what I would get for it.

992
00:52:53,662 --> 00:52:54,562
Here.

993
00:52:55,074 --> 00:52:56,130
Put it on again.

994
00:52:57,478 --> 00:52:58,747
You put it on.

995
00:53:33,356 --> 00:53:34,400
Want to dance?

996
00:53:34,827 --> 00:53:35,613
Yes.

997
00:53:59,516 --> 00:54:00,516
What's your name?

998
00:54:00,554 --> 00:54:01,644
Gabrielle.

999
00:54:01,644 --> 00:54:02,750
They call me Gabby.

1000
00:54:02,790 --> 00:54:03,580
Married?

1001
00:54:03,929 --> 00:54:04,515
No.

1002
00:54:04,570 --> 00:54:05,488
Widowed?

1003
00:54:05,542 --> 00:54:06,229
No.

1004
00:54:06,284 --> 00:54:06,957
Why not?

1005
00:54:07,662 --> 00:54:08,642
Who are you with?

1006
00:54:08,680 --> 00:54:09,722
My fiance.

1007
00:54:09,798 --> 00:54:10,725
What is he like?

1008
00:54:10,778 --> 00:54:11,632
Generous.

1009
00:54:12,723 --> 00:54:13,820
Stuck being at the hotel?

1010
00:54:13,820 --> 00:54:14,771
I let him.

1011
00:54:16,893 --> 00:54:18,207
What are you laughing at?

1012
00:54:18,207 --> 00:54:19,410
It's nothing.

1013
00:54:19,582 --> 00:54:21,243
-Too bad.
-Too bad?

1014
00:54:21,307 --> 00:54:22,928
Too bad I don't know you better.

1015
00:54:22,988 --> 00:54:23,868
Why?

1016
00:54:23,909 --> 00:54:25,661
Because I will slap your face.

1017
00:54:26,017 --> 00:54:28,476
When people laugh around me, I like to know why.

1018
00:54:35,189 --> 00:54:37,659
This all reminds me of when I was a kid.

1019
00:54:38,343 --> 00:54:40,148
We used to dance in the streets

1020
00:54:40,182 --> 00:54:42,979
on holidays, New Years, first of May.

1021
00:54:42,979 --> 00:54:44,635
14th of July.

1022
00:54:45,109 --> 00:54:46,093
Why do you know?

1023
00:54:46,132 --> 00:54:47,419
What do you think I was doing?

1024
00:54:47,892 --> 00:54:51,159
Too bad you weren't in my
 neighbourhood, Rue de la Bruyre

1025
00:54:51,159 --> 00:54:52,272
Rue de la Bruyre?

1026
00:54:52,312 --> 00:54:53,075
That's where I lived.

1027
00:54:53,075 --> 00:54:54,588
I went to school on the hill.

1028
