That was almost next door to me.

1029
00:54:56,899 --> 00:54:57,866
No.

1030
00:55:07,475 --> 00:55:08,261
Let's go out.

1031
00:55:09,358 --> 00:55:10,028
Where to?

1032
00:55:10,076 --> 00:55:11,079
To the terrace.

1033
00:55:14,751 --> 00:55:16,120
Can you see the harbor?

1034
00:55:16,120 --> 00:55:17,196
You can see Montmartre.

1035
00:55:17,325 --> 00:55:18,587
And Les Champs-lyses.

1036
00:55:18,626 --> 00:55:19,918
And Place Blanche.

1037
00:55:20,607 --> 00:55:22,190
I love Place Blanche.

1038
00:55:23,489 --> 00:55:24,456
Oh, I can't.

1039
00:55:24,694 --> 00:55:26,248
I can't leave my friends.

1040
00:55:29,925 --> 00:55:31,077
But I'll come back.

1041
00:55:31,395 --> 00:55:32,108
When?

1042
00:55:32,153 --> 00:55:33,627
As soon as I can.

1043
00:55:33,656 --> 00:55:34,334
When?

1044
00:55:35,756 --> 00:55:36,738
Tomorrow.

1045
00:55:37,539 --> 00:55:38,751
How can I be sure?

1046
00:55:39,582 --> 00:55:41,153
I never break a promise.

1047
00:55:45,038 --> 00:55:45,968
Let me go.

1048
00:55:47,125 --> 00:55:48,002
Why should I?

1049
00:55:49,203 --> 00:55:50,334
'Cause I ask you.

1050
00:55:51,791 --> 00:55:52,816
Say please.

1051
00:55:54,731 --> 00:55:55,808
You're rude.

1052
00:55:57,644 --> 00:55:58,526
Am I?

1053
00:56:07,185 --> 00:56:08,301
I'll be expecting you.

1054
00:56:09,380 --> 00:56:09,856
Here.

1055
00:56:10,883 --> 00:56:13,564
It would be nice if we could meet at Place Blanche.

1056
00:56:23,749 --> 00:56:25,324
Well, what about Pierrot?

1057
00:56:25,645 --> 00:56:26,868
I don't know.

1058
00:56:27,208 --> 00:56:28,841
Didn't you go down to find him?

1059
00:56:29,038 --> 00:56:30,977
I didn't want to leave you alone.

1060
00:56:31,007 --> 00:56:32,938
I'm not alone. I'm with madame.

1061
00:56:32,998 --> 00:56:34,164
Do as I told you.

1062
00:56:38,929 --> 00:56:39,664
Pierrot.

1063
00:56:41,382 --> 00:56:42,838
Where is he?
Who?

1064
00:56:42,838 --> 00:56:44,338
Regis. Where is he?

1065
00:56:45,782 --> 00:56:46,331
Come on.

1066
00:56:47,368 --> 00:56:48,656
They got me, Pepe.

1067
00:56:48,706 --> 00:56:49,564
The police.

1068
00:56:49,779 --> 00:56:51,410
I didn't listen to you.

1069
00:56:51,410 --> 00:56:52,343
I'll help you.

1070
00:57:46,763 --> 00:57:47,772
No. No.

1071
00:57:47,837 --> 00:57:48,450
No.

1072
00:57:48,969 --> 00:57:49,656
No.

