No.

1079
00:57:59,344 --> 00:58:00,247
No.

1080
00:58:08,571 --> 00:58:09,660
No.

1081
00:58:11,923 --> 00:58:13,581
Oh, no.

1082
00:59:25,679 --> 00:59:26,677
Pierrot?

1083
00:59:28,403 --> 00:59:29,692
There's no sense to it.

1084
00:59:29,945 --> 00:59:31,251
That's what they said.

1085
00:59:31,822 --> 00:59:32,414
They?

1086
00:59:32,995 --> 00:59:33,503
Those people.

